@startuml
title Canonical Proof Spine
left to right direction

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 18
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam ArrowThickness 2

skinparam package {
  BackgroundColor #f8fafc
  BorderColor #334155
  FontColor #0f172a
}

skinparam rectangle {
  BorderColor #334155
  FontColor #0f172a
}

skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #fff7ed
  BorderColor #c2410c
  FontColor #7c2d12
}

rectangle "Real stack source\nConcreteClosureStack\n[formal source]" as RealStack #dbeafe
rectangle "Strong quadratic forcing\nContractionForcesQuadraticStrong\n[proved]\nActive seam/bottleneck layer" as StrongCQ #dcfce7
rectangle "Lorentz / signature bridge\nContractionQuadraticToSignatureBridgeTheorem\n[proved + bridge]" as SigBridge #dcfce7
rectangle "Clifford bridge\nQuadraticToCliffordBridgeTheorem\n[proved + bridge]" as CliffBridge #dcfce7
rectangle "Canonical contraction -> Clifford bundle\nCanonicalContractionToCliffordBridgeTheorem\n[canonical assembly]" as CliffBundle #fef3c7
rectangle "Full closure instance\nPhysicsClosureFullInstance\n[current canonical closure package]" as FullClosure #fef3c7
rectangle "Unified theorem owner\nUnifiedPhysicsTheorem\n[strong claim owner]" as UnifiedOwner #fef3c7
rectangle "Abstract/canonical seam owner\nPhysicsUnificationToCanonicalClosureAdapter\n[adapter theorem owner]" as AdapterOwner #fef3c7
rectangle "Atom/chemistry recovery carrier\nAtomicChemistryRecoveryTheorem\n[packaging + bridge owner]" as AtomOwner #fef3c7
rectangle "Minimal credible closure\nMinimalCrediblePhysicsClosureShiftInstance\n[current milestone]" as MinimalCredible #fef3c7
rectangle "Known-limits GR bridge\nKnownLimitsGRBridgeTheorem\n[bridge, not full recovery]" as GRBridge #fee2e2
rectangle "Known-limits QFT bridge\nKnownLimitsQFTBridgeTheorem\n[bridge, not full recovery]" as QFTBridge #fee2e2

RealStack --> StrongCQ : source stack
StrongCQ --> SigBridge : signature route
StrongCQ --> CliffBridge : quadratic route
SigBridge --> CliffBundle : compatible Lorentz side
CliffBridge --> CliffBundle : compatible Clifford side
CliffBundle --> FullClosure : canonical assembly
FullClosure --> UnifiedOwner : theorem-owned strong claim
UnifiedOwner --> AdapterOwner : abstract/canonical seam
UnifiedOwner --> AtomOwner : atom/chemistry interpretation layer
FullClosure --> MinimalCredible : bounded milestone package
FullClosure --> GRBridge : downstream bridge
FullClosure --> QFTBridge : downstream bridge

note top of StrongCQ
If a reader wants the current formal center of gravity,
start here after the real stack source.
This is where seam quality still matters most.
end note

note bottom of MinimalCredible
This is the best current milestone package,
not a finished unified theory.
end note

note bottom of UnifiedOwner
This is where the strong repo-native claim lives now.
It does not erase the remaining proof gates.
end note

note bottom of AtomOwner
This carries the strongest current atom/chemistry layer.
It still keeps explicit recovery gates open.
end note

note bottom of GRBridge
Read as "known-limits bridge surface".
Do not upgrade to full GR recovery.
end note

note bottom of QFTBridge
Read as "known-limits bridge surface".
Do not upgrade to full QFT recovery.
end note

legend right
|= Color |= Meaning |
|<#dbeafe>| source |
|<#dcfce7>| proved / theorem-bearing |
|<#fef3c7>| canonical packaging / theorem owner / milestone |
|<#fee2e2>| downstream bridge, not final recovery |
endlegend

@enduml
